4.2.3.Human Checking via Physical Knowledge and Logical Coherence.
To reduce discrepancy and hallucination in LLM-generated captions, we implement a human checking verification stage that enforces physical plausibility, scene logic, and dataset conventions before acceptance as ground truth. Four graduate-level raters conduct this review using a structured checklist and edit protocol.

